item.title: CVE-2021-39014|2024-08-04T01:58:17.609Z -- ibm -- cloud%20object%20storage%20system
item.description: IBM Cloud Object System 3.15.8.97 is vulnerable to stored cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 213650.
